subsection.def:
the term “company” means any body
                        corporate or any entity that is treated as a body corporate for tax
                        purposes;

paragraph.content:
in the case of Vietnam, the Minister of Finance or his
                                authorized
                                representative;

subsection.def:
the term “Contracting Party”
                        means the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region or Vietnam, as the context
                        requires;

paragraph.content:
any legal person, partnership or association deriving its
                                status as such from the laws in force in
                                Vietnam;

subsection.def:
the term “person” includes an
                        individual, a company, a trust, a partnership and any other body of
                        persons;

paragraph.content:
any individual who ordinarily resides in the Hong Kong Special
                                Administrative
                                Region;

subsection.content:
a mine, an oil or gas well, a quarry or any other place of
                            extraction of natural
                            resources;

a warehouse, in relation to a person supplying storage facilities
                            for others;
                            and

the use of facilities solely for the purpose of storage or display
                            of goods or merchandise belonging to the
                            enterprise;

the maintenance of a stock of goods or merchandise belonging to the
                            enterprise solely for the purpose of storage or
                            display;

the maintenance of a stock of goods or merchandise belonging to the
                            enterprise solely for the purpose of processing by another
                            enterprise;

the maintenance of a fixed place of business solely for the purpose
                            of purchasing goods or merchandise or of collecting information, for the
                            enterprise;

sales in that other Party of goods or merchandise of the same or
                        similar kind as those sold through that permanent establishment;
                        or

other business activities carried on in that other Party of the same or
                        similar kind as those effected through that permanent
                        establishment;

paragraph.content:
other financial institution the capital of which is wholly owned by
                            the Government of
                            Vietnam;

subsection.content:
the remuneration is paid by, or on behalf of, an employer who is not a
                        resident of the other Party;
                        and

a public scheme which is part of the social security system of a
                        Contracting Party;
                        or

to carry out administrative measures at variance with the laws and the
                        administrative practice of that or of the other Contracting
                        Party;

to supply information which is not obtainable under the laws or in the
                        normal course of the administration of that or of the other Contracting
                        Party;

section.content:
in respect of Hong Kong Special Administrative Region tax, for any year of
                    assessment beginning on or after 1 April in the calendar year next following
                    that in which the notice is given;

subsection.content:
to carry out administrative measures at variance with the laws and
                    administrative practice of that or of the other Contracting
                    Party;

to supply information which is not obtainable under the laws or in the
                    normal course of the administration of that or of the other Contracting
                    Party;

section.content:
in respect of Hong Kong Special Administrative Region tax, for any year of
                assessment beginning on or after 1 April in the calendar year next following that in
                which this Protocol enters into force;
